channel.title: Who will win the war?
channel.description:
Imagine, Russia and the US come to a war. They both know that they can't use big atomic bombs because that will destroy themselves too. Now, who will win this war? Not only vote, but also explain why you chose that. So this can turn into a discussion. Yes I'm bored lol.
I think Russia will win. That's because Russia is quite a good allie (sp?) with China, and when it comes to a war they will help eachother. The US has a few allies in Europe, but that wont be of much importance. And if you look in the history books, noone has ever defeated Russia. Napoleon, who owned the rest of the known world, got defeated badly. And also Germany lost from them.
